{"tid":2130590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅冠聰：懲處陸續有來","createTime":"2020-07-29T09:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T10:22:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8fbcb39368f0ee0e03e587a0dd73772d39fc2c26","tid":2130590,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:56:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200729/MMW2BCW6BBCTIK3N4QWAY6CUJY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200729%2FMMW2BCW6BBCTIK3N4QWAY6CUJY%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6YMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=1cd6f3f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200729%2FMMW2BCW6BBCTIK3N4QWAY6CUJY%2F&h=0ec808bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200729/MMW2BCW6BBCTIK3N4QWAY6CUJY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰：懲處陸續有來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Gp04-JsA5txe6zeJYAZ-bSxfy7g=/190x142/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F7AU6LGNYRTYMS5XENVWJJUMMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGp04-JsA5txe6zeJYAZ-bSxfy7g%3D%2F190x142%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF7AU6LGNYRTYMS5XENVWJJUMMA.jpg&h=2bfeefe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅冠聰<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】行政會議召集人陳智思遭一美資銀行關閉戶口，並透露香港高官面對同樣問題，雖然陳指此事與港版國安法實施及美國制裁無關，但政界並不盡信，認為是制裁行動一部份，預料尚有其他人步陳智思後塵。<br />\n<br />\n陳智思在去年中《逃犯條例》修訂風波爆發期間接受外媒訪問時，曾指政府認為向示威者作出更多讓步、..............................<br />\n<br />\n身在英國的羅冠聰接受查詢時表示，相信外國機構...................................。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張崑陽：紀律部隊頭目受關注<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：銀行家為逃亡在所不惜<br />\n<br />\n民間外交網絡前發言人張崑陽在facebook引述《金融時報》報道，.........................................「相信特區官員，行政會議成員和紀律部隊頭目已受美方特別關注」。"},{"pid":"df0af69e879ab189796cef86436d192d2679627e","tid":2130590,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:58:29.000Z","msg":"聰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af439a1745e5da6105df78f17c5698f618f00be","tid":2130590,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:58:55.000Z","msg":"張崑陽：紀律部隊頭目受關注"},{"pid":"e45f45f266128f62196261643ac7e5246e95a4ca","tid":2130590,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:58:56.000Z","msg":"基本法腐乳就快食晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb5ff188d81d623dc7f57d6175ab2e8ccdefae5","tid":2130590,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:58:59.000Z","msg":"牙聰呢排咁搶口唔驚國安法？"},{"pid":"bb25692cde9643639f75bd6915c439b1e0c91ff2","tid":2130590,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2fb5ff188d81d623dc7f57d6175ab2e8ccdefae5","tid":2130590,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:58:59.000Z","msg":"牙聰呢排咁搶口唔驚國安法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:01:43.000Z","msg":"預咗唔返香港啦"},{"pid":"d80d858ff9822b5602deae68fca45908a74ad958","tid":2130590,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kJ0Dcg3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkJ0Dcg3.gif&h=03732d30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44b5be96a61cb7b9cd6457a5b455e816a2ccaab9","tid":2130590,"uid":321255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}